Title:          balsa.tcz
Description:    Balsa is an e-mail client for GNOME.
Version:        2.4.7
Author:         Various
Original-site:  http://pawsa.fedorapeople.org/balsa/
Copying-policy: GPL-3
Size:		1M
Extension_by:   Arslan S.
Comments:       Edit-->Preferences & modify incoming/outgoing server settings
		A typical gmail setup:
		incoming: 	IMAP: imap.gmail.com:993 (recommended)
				POP3: pop3.gmail.com:995
				Required SSL
		outgoing: 	smtp.gmail.com:587
				Required TLS
		
		A typical hotmail setup:
		incoming: 	pop3.live.com:995
				Required SSL
		outgoing: 	smtp.live.com:587
				Required TLS
		
		aspell-en & gnome-icon-theme are recommended.
		
		This extension has recursive deps.
		This extension is PPI compatible.
